videos.description: Sasha Stefanovic is feeling it early against Virginia, knocking down a trio of 3-pointers to score Purdue's first nine points of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Purdue's Stefanovic gets hot from deep early) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Purdue's Stefanovic gets hot from deep early

videos.description: Purdue's Jahaad Proctor pulls up from just inside the arc and sinks a tough jump shot despite having a hand in his face.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Proctor beats shot clock with tough pull-up jumper) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Proctor beats shot clock with tough pull-up jumper

videos.description: Matt Haarms sets a screen then pops out beyond the arc and drains his second 3-pointer of the night to put Purdue up by 18.
videos.headline: Purdue's Haarms fired up after 3-ball
